In [42]:
rho_air = 1.22 # Density of air in kg m-3
ds['ws10'] = np.sqrt(ds.u10**2+ds.v10**2)
ds['utau'] = rho_air * ds.cd * ds.ws10 * ds.u10
ds['vtau'] = rho_air * ds.cd * ds.ws10 * ds.v10
ds.utau.isel(Time=12).plot.contourf(robust=True)

dx, dy = 10000, 10000
curl = mpcalc.vorticity(ds.utau.values * units('m/s'), 
                        ds.vtau.values * units('m/s'),
                        dx=dx* units.meter, 
                        dy=dy* units.meter)
ds['curl_tau'] = xr.DataArray(curl, coords=ds.utau.coords)
